ls about the number coding scheme, anti-plastic ordinance, silent night ordinance, and responsible pet ownership. Each entry includes a concise description of the regulation and, where applicable, the associated penalty. Next, I\'ll be adding the education tab elements.\n\n\n**Adding cultural sites**\n\nI\'m now focusing on the education tab, beginning with details for University of Baguio, University of the Cordilleras, and Teachers Camp. Then, I\'m integrating the culture tab elements, starting with Panagbenga, including \"A Season of Blooming,\" \"Grand Floral Floats,\" and \"Woven Through Generations\". I am organizing the information to ensure a cohesive presentation of the city\'s cultural richness.\n\n\n"
