          type: UNIFIED_DIFF_LINE_TYPE_INSERT
        }
        lines {
          text: "    longText: \'Asin Road stands as the woodcarving capitol of Baguio City. Native Ifugao artists utilize uprooted mahogany trunks and sustainable acacia woods to sculpt lifelike figures representing native highlanders, woodland fauna, and abstract nature concepts, demonstrating deep Cordilleran environmental stewardship.\'"
