  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Considering Component Organization**\n\nI\'ve got standard TypeScript interfaces and static data now. Next, I\'m leaning toward organizing the tab logic into modular components within a `/src/components/` folder. This structure promises cleaner, more readable code and avoids large, unwieldy files.\n\n\n**Defining Component Hierarchy**\n\nI\'ve specified the planned components: Header, Footer, BookingPortal, ItineraryEngine, and DetailModal. I\'m focusing on their respective functionalities and how they fit together to create a cohesive user experience. The ItineraryEngine is particularly interesting, as I\'m thinking of building it to dynamically generate personalized weekend trip itineraries based on user input. I\'m also planning a DetailModal for displaying rich supplemental data.\n\n\n"
