    thinking: "**Defining the Interface**\n\nI\'ve got the modular codebase set up and it\'s looking extraordinary. Currently, I\'m reviewing the `src/App.tsx` file. Now, I\'m focusing on defining the screens. I want to start with a beautiful Explore (Home) screen, with a hero header banner with a cover photograph.\n\n\n**Refining the Sections**\n\nI\'m now zeroing in on the content within each defined screen. Specifically, I\'m working on the design for an explore screen with an interactive section and card layouts. I\'ve designed several sections to feature, which I\'ve started building out and iterating on to perfect the details, hover states, and detail views. I\'m focusing on \"Ready for the Chill?\" and crafting a CTA block.\n\n\n"
